catalogDescription
	^ 'Pillar is a wiki-like syntax, its document model, a parser for it, and a set of exporters (e.g., HTML, LaTeX, Markdown...). Pillar is primarily used as the wiki syntax behind the *Pier CMS>http://piercms.com*. Pillar is also being used to write books: e.g., *the Enterprise Pharo book>http://books.pharo.org/*.'